---
/**
 * ASCII horizontal rule — a single line of box-drawing dashes in the faint
 * foreground color. Replaces native <hr> for visual section breaks while
 * staying in the terminal aesthetic.
 *
 * Constitution III: styling is Tailwind utilities only; this component exists
 * to dedupe the utility chain + 120-character dash literal across the home page.
 */
---

<div
  class="text-fg-faint overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap select-none my-6"
  aria-hidden="true"
>────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</div>
